WITH RECURSIVE customer_order_summary AS (
    SELECT 
        c.c_custkey,
        c.c_name,
        o.o_orderkey,
        o.o_orderdate,
        SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_spent,
        SUM(l.l_quantity) AS total_items
    FROM 
        customer c
    JOIN 
        orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey
    JOIN 
        lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey
    WHERE 
        o.o_orderdate BETWEEN DATE '1996-01-01' AND DATE '1996-12-31'
    GROUP BY 
        c.c_custkey, c.c_name, o.o_orderkey, o.o_orderdate
),

supplier_performance AS (
    SELECT 
        s.s_suppkey,
        s.s_name,
        AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS avg_supply_cost,
        COUNT(DISTINCT ps.ps_partkey) AS supplied_parts
    FROM 
        supplier s
    LEFT JOIN 
        partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
    GROUP BY 
        s.s_suppkey, s.s_name
),

top_customers AS (
    SELECT 
        c.c_custkey, 
        c.c_name, 
        SUM(co.total_spent) AS total_customer_spent
    FROM 
        customer_order_summary co
    JOIN 
        customer c ON co.c_custkey = c.c_custkey
    GROUP BY 
        c.c_custkey, c.c_name
    ORDER BY 
        total_customer_spent DESC
    LIMIT 10
)

SELECT 
    tc.c_name AS customer_name,
    tc.total_customer_spent,
    sp.s_name AS supplier_name,
    sp.avg_supply_cost,
    sp.supplied_parts
FROM 
    top_customers tc
CROSS JOIN 
    supplier_performance sp
WHERE 
    tc.total_customer_spent > (SELECT AVG(total_spent) FROM customer_order_summary)
ORDER BY 
    tc.total_customer_spent DESC, sp.avg_supply_cost ASC

(SELECT "s1"."s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "s1"."s_name" AS "S_NAME", AVG("partsupp"."ps_supplycost") AS "AVG_SUPPLY_COST", COUNT(DISTINCT "partsupp"."ps_partkey") AS "SUPPLIED_PARTS"
FROM "s1"
LEFT JOIN "partsupp" ON "s1"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "s1"."s_suppkey", "s1"."s_name") AS "t7"
WHERE "t5"."TOTAL_CUSTOMER_SPENT" > (((SELECT AVG(SUM("lineitem0"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem0"."l_discount")))
FROM "customer" AS "customer1"
INNER JOIN "orders" AS "orders0" ON "customer1"."c_custkey" = "orders0"."o_custkey"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" AS "lineitem0" ON "orders0"."o_orderkey" = "lineitem0"."l_orderkey"
WHERE "orders0"."o_orderdate" >= DATE '1996-01-01' AND "orders0"."o_orderdate" <= DATE '1996-12-31'
GROUP BY "customer1"."c_custkey", "customer1"."c_name", "orders0"."o_orderkey", "orders0"."o_orderdate")))
ORDER BY "t5"."TOTAL_CUSTOMER_SPENT" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t7"."AVG_SUPPLY_COST"

SELECT COALESCE("ps_partkey", "ps_partkey") AS "ps_partkey", "ps_suppkey", "ps_availqty", "ps_supplycost", "ps_comment"
FROM "partsupp"

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."C_NAME", "t5"."C_NAME") AS "CUSTOMER_NAME", "t5"."TOTAL_CUSTOMER_SPENT", "t7"."S_NAME" AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", "t7"."AVG_SUPPLY_COST", "t7"."SUPPLIED_PARTS"
FROM (SELECT "customer0"."c_custkey" AS "C_CUSTKEY", "customer0"."c_name" AS "C_NAME", SUM("t2"."TOTAL_SPENT") AS "TOTAL_CUSTOMER_SPENT"
FROM (SELECT "customer"."c_custkey" AS "C_CUSTKEY", "customer"."c_name" AS "C_NAME", "orders"."o_orderkey" AS "O_ORDERKEY", "orders"."o_orderdate" AS "O_ORDERDATE", SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_SPENT", SUM("lineitem"."l_quantity") AS "TOTAL_ITEMS"
FROM "customer"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "orders"."o_custkey"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" ON "orders"."o_orderkey" = "lineitem"."l_orderkey"
WHERE "orders"."o_orderdate" >= DATE '1996-01-01' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" <= DATE '1996-12-31'
GROUP BY "customer"."c_custkey", "customer"."c_name", "orders"."o_orderkey", "orders"."o_orderdate") AS "t2"
INNER JOIN "customer" AS "customer0" ON "t2"."C_CUSTKEY" = "customer0"."c_custkey"
GROUP BY "customer0"."c_custkey", "customer0"."c_name"
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t5",
(SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "supplier"."s_name" AS "S_NAME", AVG("s1"."ps_supplycost") AS "AVG_SUPPLY_COST", COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."ps_partkey") AS "SUPPLIED_PARTS"
FROM "supplier"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "s1"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name") AS "t7"
WHERE "t5"."TOTAL_CUSTOMER_SPENT" > (((SELECT AVG(SUM("lineitem0"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem0"."l_discount")))
FROM "customer" AS "customer1"
INNER JOIN "orders" AS "orders0" ON "customer1"."c_custkey" = "orders0"."o_custkey"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" AS "lineitem0" ON "orders0"."o_orderkey" = "lineitem0"."l_orderkey"
WHERE "orders0"."o_orderdate" >= DATE '1996-01-01' AND "orders0"."o_orderdate" <= DATE '1996-12-31'
GROUP BY "customer1"."c_custkey", "customer1"."c_name", "orders0"."o_orderkey", "orders0"."o_orderdate")))
ORDER BY "t5"."TOTAL_CUSTOMER_SPENT" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t7"."AVG_SUPPLY_COST"
